dct_title_s: Geologic map of the Smith Mountain quadrangle, Monterey and Fresno Counties, California
dct_description_sm: by Thomas W. Dibblee, Jr. ; edited by John A. Minch.
Relief shown by contours and spot heights.
"Topographic base map from available USGS 7.5-minute quadrangle Smith Mountain, CA 1969, photoinspected1981, DMA 1856 II SE--Series V895."
Includes quadrangle location map, index to adjacent 7.5 minute quadrangles, and index to sources of geology.
